terest, relies on some basic facts about the \\'etale\nfundamental group of an algebraic variety.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Nov 2012 05:53:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Nov 2012 16:34:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2012 18:15:41 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2013 05:11:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-04"}
